headline: Amy Friedrich President of Benefits & Protection to Speak at 2025 KBW Insurance Conference
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, August 07, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) announced today that Amy Friedrich, president of Benefits & Protection, will participate in a fireside chat at the KBW Insurance Conference on Thursday, Sept. 4, 2025, beginning at approximately 3:05 p.m. Eastern Time. Friedrich will participate in a question-and-answer session covering a variety of industry and company specific topics.

headline: 2025 Principal® Charity Classic Raised Record $10.6 Million for Iowa Youth
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, August 07, 2025--The Principal® Charity Classic today announced the 2025 tournament raised a record $10.6 million in support of Iowa youth. The annual PGA TOUR Champions event in Des Moines has raised more than $73 million for Iowa children’s charities since Principal Financial Group® became the title sponsor in 2007.
